interpretation: The "rice cracker" card represents simplicity, minimalism, and the basic necessities of life. It reminds us to appreciate the small things and find joy in the simple pleasures. This card encourages us to take a step back from the chaos and complexity of modern life and focus on the essentials. It can also signify a need for patience and perseverance, as rice crackers require time and effort to make. Overall, the "rice cracker" card reminds us to embrace simplicity and find contentment in the present moment.
